Pierre de Saint Phalle: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 21, 2017 5:20 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Aetos Capital Multi Strategy Arbitrage Fund LLC



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Pierre   de Saint Phalle  Manager, Aetos Capital Multi Strategy Arbitrage Fund LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships69--
Background

		Mr. Pierre de Saint Phalle has been Consultant of Promontory Financial Group since March 2005. Mr. de Saint Phalle has been Independent Manager of Aetos Capital Opportunities Fund Llc, Aetos Capital Multi Strategy Arbitrage Fund LLC and Aetos Capital Long/Short Strategies Fund LLC since 2002. He served as a Partner of Davis Polk & Wardwell from January 1983 to October 2000. Mr. de Saint Phalle also served as a Managing Director and Chief Legal Officer of iFormation Group ... from November 2000 to November 2003. He has been the Chairman of Atlantic Whitehall Funds since January 2004.Read Full Background




Corporate Headquarters
875 Third AvenueNew York, New York 10022United StatesPhone: 212-201-2500Fax: --
